    <p>Set in the 1980s, <em>Stranger Things</em> follows a group of young friends in Hawkins, Indiana. When a boy named Will disappears, a mysterious girl with supernatural powers appears. Together, they uncover secret government experiments and a terrifying alternate dimension called the Upside Down.</p>
