  <main class="section">
    <h2>Main Characters</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Eleven:</strong> A girl with psychokinetic powers.</li>
      <li><strong>Mike:</strong> Loyal friend and Eleven's love interest.</li>
      <li><strong>Will:</strong> Kidnapped into the Upside Down.</li>
      <li><strong>Joyce:</strong> Will's determined mother.</li>
      <li><strong>Hopper:</strong> The town's chief of police.</li>
    </ul>
